OL,3,CKing's official birthday to be
OL,4,Ccelebrated with Trooping the Colour
OL,6,FThe nation will celebrate the King's
OL,7,Fofficial birthday with the famous
OL,8,FTrooping the Colour ceremony staged by
OL,9,Fsome of the military's most
OL,10,Fprestigious regiments.
OL,12,FThe royal family will join thousands
OL,13,Fof spectators in Whitehall for the
OL,14,Fannual event that will bring together
OL,15,Fthe three services to mark Charles'
OL,16,Fanniversary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
