OL,3,CKing's official birthday to be
OL,4,Ccelebrated with Trooping the Colour
OL,6,FGuardsmen in their scarlet tunics and
OL,7,Fbearskin caps will deliver a display
OL,8,Fof precision marching on Horse Guards
OL,9,FParade, honed over weeks of practice
OL,10,Fand part of their ceremonial duties
OL,11,Fwhen not fighting soldiers.
OL,13,FThe national celebration is one of the
OL,14,Fhighlights of the royal calendar and
OL,15,Flater will feature the royal family
OL,16,Fassembled on Buckingham Palace's
OL,17,Fbalcony for the traditional fly-past
OL,18,Fof RAF aircraft.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
