OL,3,CKing's official birthday to be
OL,4,Ccelebrated with Trooping the Colour
OL,6,FThe colour ` regimental flag ` being
OL,7,Ftrooped this year is the King's Colour
OL,8,Fof the Grenadier Guards presented by
OL,9,Fthe King earlier this week during a
OL,10,FBuckingham Palace ceremony and it will
OL,11,Fbe escorted during Saturday's
OL,12,Fspectacle by guardsmen from the King's
OL,13,FCompany.
OL,15,FThe new Defence Secretary Dan Jarvis
OL,16,Fis expected to be among the spectators
OL,17,Fwith other senior cabinet members,
OL,18,Fincluding the Prime Minister, after
OL,19,Fhis predecessor John Healey quit on
OL,20,FThursday over a dispute about long-
OL,21,Fterm funding for the military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
