OL,3,CKing's official birthday to be
OL,4,Ccelebrated with Trooping the Colour
OL,6,FHe told the company: "Since Easter
OL,7,Fyou've been practising rigidly and I
OL,8,Fcan hear from Buckingham Palace the
OL,9,Fsound of the drums thumping away
OL,10,Fregularly so I know you're all
OL,11,Fmarching up and down trying to get
OL,12,Fready for the parade."
OL,14,FThe King went on to say: "...ever
OL,15,Fsince the last 370 years of your
OL,16,Fexistence you have made us all in this
OL,17,Fcountry so incredibly proud of your
OL,18,Feffort, your service and your
OL,19,Fsacrifice over all those years and I
OL,20,Ffeel very proud and privileged to be
OL,21,Fhere."
